### Get Equipment
GET {{Api_HostAddress}}/Api/v1/Equipments?$filter=Id eq b79d3481-df2c-4287-a340-01d4c7a86edd&$expand=Packs
Content-Type: application/json

### Get Equipment
GET {{Api_HostAddress}}/Api/v1/Equipments(b79d3481-df2c-4287-a340-01d4c7a86edd)?$expand=Packs
Content-Type: application/json

### Get All Equipment
GET {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/Equipments?$expand=Packs
Content-Type: application/json